  "title": "Operator/ General Worker",
  "description": "<p><strong>HAID BIOTECHNOLOGY INDUSTRY (SINGAPORE) PTE. LTD. </strong>is seeking a detail-oriented and experienced Warehouse Operations Executive<strong> </strong>to join our new startup team in Singapore. The ideal candidate will be overseeing and optimizing the end-to-end warehouse operations, ensuring efficiency, accuracy, and safety in all processes.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><br />1. Responsible for daily operations on the feed production line, such as feeding, handling, packaging, and palletizing.<br />2. Perform basic operation and routine checks of production equipment according to regulations.<br />3.Maintain cleanliness of the work area and strictly adhere to production safety and food hygiene standards.<br />4. Complete other related production tasks assigned by the supervisor.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p><strong>Age / Physical:</strong> Good health and capable of performing physical labor.<br /><strong>Experience:</strong> No prior experience required; on-the-job training will be provided. Experience in manufacturing or food processing plants is advantageous.<br /><strong>Attitude:</strong> Hard-working and diligent, responsible, able to follow work instructions, and possess good teamwork spirit.<br /><strong>Other:</strong> Able to adapt to working environments that may involve dust and noise, as commonly found in feed production.</p><p><strong>Language: </strong>Good command of both verbal Mandarin to liaise with Mandarin-speaking business associates.</p><p>• Company website: https://www.haid.com.cn/</p>",
